Package com.carrentalsystem.entity

Class Vehicle

java.lang.Object
com.carrentalsystem.entity.Vehicle
public class Vehicle extends Object
The Vehicle class represents a vehicle in a car rental system. It encapsulates information such as vehicle ID, make, model, year, daily rate, status, passenger capacity, and engine capacity.
